text: Uss waqt aziz-e-misir ki biwi ney kaha yehi hain jin kay baray mein tum mujhay tanay dey rahi thin mein ney her chand iss say apna matlab hasil kerna chaha lekin yeh baal baal bacha raha aur jo kuch mein iss say keh rahi hun agar yeh na keray ga to yaqeenan yeh qaid ker diya jayega aur be-shak yeh boht hi bey izzat hoga
